{"word":"συρρέω","slug":"συρρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συρρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ρεύσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-ερρύηκα</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-ερρύην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to flow together</i> or <i>in one stream</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of men, <i>to flow</i> or <i>stream together</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to float together with</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}